text:
I would just go to school and listen to
   everybody's voices—I just went into school knowing just basic English, like
   "Can I go to the restroom?" Or, "I'm hungry," or "I don't understand."
   Those were the three words I would know and I would just listen to a lot of
   voices and what they would say and I just quickly grabbed on to it.
 
 
   Anita:
name: Melani
